metadata.name: Map of Florence
metadata.description:
Hand drawn aerial illustration of the centre of Florence in Italy.

Scanned from a hand drawn pen and ink drawing, this artwork measures 12000 DPI and comes with a signed giclee print.

The map was drawn in 2021 and represents one of my favourite subjects to draw, an aerial view, highlighting the hundreds of different rooftops that define the streets in this beautiful city.
